{"tid":209464,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"router與iphone問題","createTime":"2017-04-20T08:30:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T10:59:51.000Z","uid":107400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f6e55576a373cf2ff29981e16104e6adf81e54ec","tid":209464,"uid":107400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:30:48.000Z","msg":"是咁的 早排借左人地部iphone 6 plus, <br />\n咁用左陣都好地地, 但慢慢發玩wifi愈黎愈唔穩定<br />\n收到wifi signal, 但連唔到上網 ,而其他機係完全冇問題<br />\n屋企都有人用開6+ 兩年黎都冇問題,<br />\nreset過所有野都係一樣 一時上到一時上唔到,<br />\n今日搶左朋友個舊router試下機 , <br />\n亂插發現用人地個router做main(先接wan),<br />\n再由main既lan接去我原本個router射wifi,<br />\n然後又突然變番順曬 連得好好<br />\n<br />\n當中乜setting都冇改 只係鳩插 <br />\n人地個router 就set 原廠<br />\n<br />\n其實會係咩問題呢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到底係乜野壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n補充番 用電話share wifi比6+果時 佢都順 <br />\n係接屋企wifi有問題 <br />\nsorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"700929aa89d7ac735974b2e6855d7d24327bcd62","tid":209464,"uid":62722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:34:28.000Z","msg":"tp link?"},{"pid":"6b89eca1ba3185b6013404cccabbbb70792aade5","tid":209464,"uid":107400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:39:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>tp link?</blockquote><br />\n有先知呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b9cdbb6629bb0d66661aa5d783128e506f2f142","tid":209464,"uid":107400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2